57#include <cflib.h>
58
59int
60smb_smb_open_print_file(struct smb_ctx *ctx, int setuplen, int mode,
61 const char *ident, smbfh *fhp)
62{
63 struct smb_rq *rqp;
64 struct mbdata *mbp;
65 int error;
66
67 error = smb_rq_init(ctx, SMB_COM_OPEN_PRINT_FILE, 2, &rqp);
68 if (error)
69 return error;
70 mbp = smb_rq_getrequest(rqp);
71 mb_put_uint16le(mbp, setuplen);
72 mb_put_uint16le(mbp, mode);
73 smb_rq_wend(rqp);
74 mb_put_uint8(mbp, SMB_DT_ASCII);
75 smb_rq_dstring(mbp, ident);
76 error = smb_rq_simple(rqp);
77 if (!error) {
78 mbp = smb_rq_getreply(rqp);
79 mb_get_uint16(mbp, fhp);
80 }
81 smb_rq_done(rqp);
82 return error;
83}
84
85int
86smb_smb_close_print_file(struct smb_ctx *ctx, smbfh fh)
87{
88 struct smb_rq *rqp;
89 struct mbdata *mbp;
90 int error;
91
92 error = smb_rq_init(ctx, SMB_COM_CLOSE_PRINT_FILE, 0, &rqp);
93 if (error)
94 return error;
95 mbp = smb_rq_getrequest(rqp);
96 mb_put_mem(mbp, (char*)&fh, 2);
97 smb_rq_wend(rqp);
98 error = smb_rq_simple(rqp);
99 smb_rq_done(rqp);
100 return error;
101}
